data.description: Great location and flexible space can be yours with this low-maintenance home in sought-after Kernersville. Large rooms and well-planned design, make this a great choice for anyone.  Downstairs is a large family room, kitchen with stainless appliances, bonus room, large pantry and a new covered patio. This all makes for the perfect spot for friends and family to gather. Upstairs, there are 3 generously-sized bedrooms, laundry room and access to pull-down attic storage. Enjoy time around the fire pit in the backyard, letting kids or pets enjoy freedom in the fenced yard or under the shade of the covered patio. All of this located in Kernersville, with good proximity to shopping, restaurants, recreation (Salem Lake) and most areas of the Triad via 421 and I-40. Don't miss this opportunity.
